{"tid":1358854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家入嚟睇睇727對付落單警或者黑社會既方法","createTime":"2019-07-24T04:14:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T17:02:14.000Z","uid":244889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1e2dc4d702df2acc6f84a505305243673823f7d7","tid":1358854,"uid":244889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:14:58.000Z","msg":"大家見到落單既人，都掛住衝埋去打佢<br />\n而唔記得咗最緊要既一樣野<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢既身份</span><br />\n<br />\n最尾就導致嗰條友，係人係鬼都唔知<br />\n如果我地打佢果陣時，順便搵佢銀包<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">搵佢張委任證/身份證</span></span><br />\n<br />\n例如有個疑似警察入嚟打人<br />\n我哋就執行公民拘捕權<br />\n如果搵到佢張委任證<br />\n就提吓佢要<span style=\"color: red;\">下次要擺番出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n如果搵唔到佢張委任證<br />\n就搵身份證，告佢<span style=\"color: red;\">冒警</span><br />\n如果乜都搵唔到<br />\n就告佢<span style=\"color: red;\">非法入境</span><br />\n<br />\n總之抄底佢啲資料，方便日後跟進<br />\n絕對唔係攞嚟起底用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68d22b3ffedd8f48464ff5ba0135a6ef23da2a93","tid":1358854,"uid":244889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:16:12.000Z","msg":"樓主英明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下次打人會抄底身分證㗎啦"},{"pid":"9a14d246e21c5c3c8624939f9ebee05fe067dfb8","tid":1358854,"uid":244889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:16:49.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"c643747863e7e1e62294b6fe367d32382324bf3b","tid":1358854,"uid":244889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:18:42.000Z","msg":"Diu仆街開錯台"},{"pid":"ec109b535bacb277b237d46a0d51f51ae7a227ce","tid":1358854,"uid":244889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:54:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"385ce93aa46a7287a9af35b63214d7f854d77559","tid":1358854,"uid":244889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:54:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{